originalText.text: Spot was nice vibes. The DJ was amazing. The Rum punch was good. There were some areas of disappointment. They had no wine. One of my girlfriends ordered a cup of Chardonnay when we first got there, and turns out that was all the wine they had in house. The food was ok I had the shrimp and fries. Shrimp was good, just a little salty. Not a big fan of the wings. Nice place to chill out and enjoy the vibes
